        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="en">impeachment for maltreatment</skos:prefLabel>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">Public lawsuit for maltreatment of parents orphans and heiresses, defendant summoned by plaintiff via prosklesis, initiated by submitting a charge in writing to magistrate, supervised by Eponymous Archon, tried by the dikasterion, has punishment for convicted of an assessable fine, has no penalty for failed prosecution, with assessable penalty through timesis.</skos:definition>
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="grc">εἰσαγγελία κάκωσις</rdfs:label>
        <skos:prefLabel xml:lang="grc">εἰσαγγελία κάκωσις</skos:prefLabel>
