        <otv:gender>none</otv:gender>
        <otv:termDefinition>Δίκη to overturn decision of a magistrate, supervised by the Thesmothetai, tried by the dikasterion.</otv:termDefinition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="grc">Δίκη to overturn decision of a magistrate, supervised by the Thesmothetai, tried by the dikasterion.</skos:definition>
    </otv:Term>

    <otv:Term rdf:about="#ψευδομαρτυριῶν_δίκη_grc">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="grc">ψευδομαρτυριῶν δίκη</rdfs:label>
        <otv:termName>ψευδομαρτυριῶν δίκη</otv:termName>
        <otv:language>grc</otv:language>
        <otv:denotedConcept rdf:resource="#Legal_proceeding_brought_forward_by_the_injured_party_or_a_guardian_with_a_prosecutor_and_defendant_for_providing_false_witness_testimony_defendant_summoned_by_plaintiff_via_prosklesis_initiated_by_submitting_a_charge_in_writing_to_magistrate_supervised_by_the_Thesmothetai_tried_by_the_dikasterion_has_punishment_for_convicted_of_an_assessable_fine_has_penalty_of_epobelia_for_failed_prosecution_with_assessable_penalty_through_timesis"/>
        <otv:termStatus>preferred</otv:termStatus>
        <otv:partOfSpeech>none</otv:partOfSpeech>
        <otv:gender>none</otv:gender>
        <otv:termDefinition>Δίκαι ἴδιαι for providing false witness testimony, defendant summoned by plaintiff via prosklesis, initiated by submitting a charge in writing to magistrate, supervised by the Thesmothetai, tried by the dikasterion, has punishment for convicted of an assessable fine, has penalty of epobelia for failed prosecution, with assessable penalty through timesis.</otv:termDefinition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="grc">Δίκαι ἴδιαι for providing false witness testimony, defendant summoned by plaintiff via prosklesis, initiated by submitting a charge in writing to magistrate, supervised by the Thesmothetai, tried by the dikasterion, has punishment for convicted of an assessable fine, has penalty of epobelia for failed prosecution, with assessable penalty through timesis.</skos:definition>
        <otv:context xml:lang="grc">Dem. 24.131: "οὐδὲ γὰρ οἱ τῆς ξενίας ἁλισκόμενοι ἀγανακτοῦσιν ἐν τῷ οἰκήματι τούτῳ ὄντες, ἕως ἂν τῶν ψευδομαρτυριῶν ἀγωνίσωνται, ἀλλὰ μένουσιν καὶ οὐκ οἴονται δεῖν ἐγγυητὰς καταστήσαντες περιιέναι."</otv:context>
        <otv:context xml:lang="grc">Isaeus 11.46: "δίκαι γὰρ ἐνεστήκασι ψευδομαρτυρίων, κελεύει δ᾽ ὁ νόμος, ἐὰν ἁλῷ τις τῶν ψευδομαρτυρίων, πάλιν ἐξ ἀρχῆς εἶναι περὶ αὐτῶν τὰς λήξεις: τὰ δὲ τοῦ παιδὸς ὡμολογημένα καὶ ἀναμφισβήτητα καταλέλοιπε Στρατοκλῆς. ὅτι δὲ τοσαῦτά ἐστι τἀμὰ σὺν τοῖς τοῦ ἐκποιήτου ὑέος, καὶ ψευδομαρτυριῶν ἐνεστᾶσι δίκαι περὶ τῶν Ἁγνίου, λαβὲ τὰς μαρτυρίας καὶ ἀνάγνωθι."</otv:context>
    </otv:Term>

    <otv:Term rdf:about="#ἀσεβείας_τοῦ_σηκοῦ γραφή_grc">
        <rdfs:label xml:lang="grc">ἀσεβείας τοῦ σηκοῦ γραφή</rdfs:label>
        <otv:termName>ἀσεβείας τοῦ σηκοῦ γραφή</otv:termName>
        <otv:language>grc</otv:language>
        <otv:denotedConcept rdf:resource="#Legal_proceeding_brought_forward_by_anyone_who_wishes_with_a_prosecutor_and_defendant_initiated_by_submitting_a_charge_in_writing_to_magistrate_defendant_summoned_by_plaintiff_via_prosklesis_has_penalty_of_1000_drachmas_for_failed_prosecution_for_destruction_of_sacred_olive_trees_supervised_by_Basileus_tried_by_the_Council_of_the_Areopagus_has_punishment_for_convicted_of_death_with_non-assessable_penalty"/>
        <otv:termStatus>preferred</otv:termStatus>
        <otv:partOfSpeech>none</otv:partOfSpeech>
        <otv:gender>none</otv:gender>
        <otv:termDefinition>Γραφή for destruction of sacred olive trees, supervised by Basileus, tried by the Council of the Areopagus, has punishment for convicted of death, with non-assessable penalty.</otv:termDefinition>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="grc">Γραφή for destruction of sacred olive trees, supervised by Basileus, tried by the Council of the Areopagus, has punishment for convicted of death, with non-assessable penalty.</skos:definition>
        <otv:context xml:lang="grc">Lys. 7.2: "οὕτω δ᾽ ἄπορος ὁ ἀγών μοι καθέστηκεν, ὥστε ἀπεγράφην τὸ μὲν πρῶτον ἐλάαν ἐκ τῆς γῆς ἀφανίζειν, καὶ πρὸς τοὺς ἐωνημένους τοὺς καρποὺς τῶν μορίων πυνθανόμενοι προσῇσαν: ἐπειδὴ δ᾽ ἐκ τούτου τοῦ τρόπου ἀδικοῦντά με οὐδὲν εὑρεῖν ἐδυνήθησαν, νυνί με σηκόν φασιν1 ἀφανίζειν, ἡγούμενοι ἐμοὶ μὲν ταύτην τὴν αἰτίαν ἀπορωτάτην εἶναι ἀπελέγξαι,2 αὐτοῖς δὲ ἐξεῖναι μᾶλλον ὅ τι ἂν βούλωνται λέγειν."</otv:context>
    </otv:Term>

